lead_paragraph: Hillary Rodham Clinton gave Jon Stewart no hints about whether she will run for president, but acknowledged during Tuesday's taping of "The Daily Show" that the speculation surrounding her possible candidacy has become "a cottage industry."

headline.main: No Hints From Hillary Clinton on 'The Daily Show'
